{"title":"Symbols, words or sentences in reverse order","description":"This tool allows you to change the text so that all symbols, words or sentences are arranged in reverse order. To do this, select the desired section of text and click on the corresponding function.","content":"## Symbols, words or sentences in reverse order\r\nThis tool allows you to change the text so that all characters, words or sentences are arranged in reverse order. To do this, select the desired section of text and click on the corresponding function.\n\n You can also familiarize yourself with other functionality of this online [text editor](/en/editor)."}